article.description: — Collin Welp had 11 points, seven rebounds and six assists as UC Irvine defeated Boise State 58-50 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Welp scores 11 to lead UC Irvine over Boise State 58-50
article.linkText: Welp scores 11 to lead UC Irvine over Boise State 58-50
article.story: IRVINE, Calif. -- — Collin Welp had 11 points, seven rebounds and six assists as UC Irvine defeated Boise State 58-50 on Saturday night. Dawson Baker had 10 points for UC Irvine (1-1). Austin Johnson added five points, eight rebounds and five blocks. Marcus Shaver, Jr. had 14 points for the Broncos (1-1). Emmanuel Akot added 11 points and seven rebounds.
